summary:
My first enb, it gives skyrim a fantasy atmosphere, IT IS NOT DESIGNED TO BE REALISTIC !!
Download the lastest enb series on Enbdev.
descriptionHtml:
It has vivid colors, no too much saturation and a good contrast, in my opinion. It comes with a SweetFx and an effect.txt, you can adjust lettrebox in the shader window in the GUI. I tried to make nights darks and days clears.
   If you have any problem, please post a comment on my videos or on the nexus. Also, i don't know if the Dof is working well, i'm playing on an Optimus laptop with a 880m and it can't activate. However, i use Dynavision.
